{"tid":1623472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咁多人明知你哋要屌佢都要出聲","createTime":"2019-10-04T22:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T23:11:06.000Z","uid":223407,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dd077a2c218dd361b35a058b9cc9556b55be357d","tid":1623472,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T22:41:18.000Z","msg":"我必須講，出聲嗰啲人已經好小心好客氣，你哋依然要屌佢哋，人哋都係好心提醒你哋，打爛人哋店舖，好大機會會有民意轉向嘅機會。我想講，呢度唔止一兩個人，明知你你唔聽人哋講嘢就屌人哋，都要出聲。<br />\n<br />\n你有冇諗過如果唔聽下大家嘅意見，同林鄭政府有乜嘢分別呢？<br />\n<br />\n聽下，唔一定要認同，但唔係一開口就屌鳩人哋，屈鳩人哋喺度割蓆。核爆都唔割蓆係唔係俾藉口你哋唔用腦？<br />\n<br />\n歡迎負皮，我都想知道究竟幾多人係唔用腦。"},{"pid":"5612c4760fbef0f60924ab4a4b5838cc3b95aa6f","tid":1623472,"uid":276839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T22:42:53.000Z","msg":"討論區唔洗太認真"},{"pid":"3646df642633f2cc61d899cddd71f55bf4c8cc3a","tid":1623472,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5612c4760fbef0f60924ab4a4b5838cc3b95aa6f","tid":1623472,"uid":276839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T22:42:53.000Z","msg":"討論區唔洗太認真"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T22:43:37.000Z","msg":"我已經打晒底。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2de9173c104058ac614f25996fbf582b00011c0","tid":1623472,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T22:47:10.000Z","msg":"和理非表示打爆完鋪頭俾其他人入去偷嘢個下先嬲<br />\n又要俾正苦屈啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3970d86092d580cab0999d5de8979ba3c0bf1e1a","tid":1623472,"uid":304052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T22:47:59.000Z","msg":"我明，明明大家都係想為件事好，唔想見到前線俾人割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0353218815377a1d6eb23b326049f2514e4b0752","tid":1623472,"uid":194398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T22:4